<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reviews - Restaurant Name</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 150px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px; /* Increased font size */
            padding: 8px 16px; /* Added padding for better clickability */
            border-radius: 4px; /* Rounded corners for links */
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease; /* Smooth transition */
        }
        nav ul li a:hover {
            background-color: #ffd700; /* Yellow background on hover */
            color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark text on hover */
        }
        .cta-button {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid #ffd700;
            color: #ffd700;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .reservation-button {
            background-color: #ffd700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .reviews-content {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .reviews-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .reviews-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .reviews-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .review-card {
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .review-avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .review-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .review-text {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #ccc;
        }
        .review-images {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .review-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        #yo{
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div><img class="logo" src="Screenshot 2024-10-02 022710.png" alt=""></div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/homepage">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/review">Reviews</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/ourmenu">Our Menu</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/offer">Offers</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <button class="reservation-button"><a href="./reservation.ejs" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">Reservation</a></button>
        </header>

        <div class="reviews-content">
            <div class="reviews-header">
                <h1>Our Clients Say</h1>
                <p>We love to hear from customers, so please leave a comment or say hello in an email.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reviews-grid">
                <div class="review-card">
                    <img class="review-avatar" src="https://www.w3schools.com/w3images/avatar2.png" alt="John Doe's Avatar">
                    <div class="review-name">John Doe</div>
                    <div class="review-text">"This is how to be fabulous since you read. Anywhere you go people image is watched. The best dishes & images done are perfect."</div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-card">
                    <img class="review-avatar" src="https://www.w3schools.com/w3images/avatar6.png" alt="Jane Smith's Avatar">
                    <div class="review-name">Jane Smith</div>
                    <div class="review-text">"I have visited this fantastic restaurant on several occasions, food is absolutely outstanding & attention to detail is in league of its own."</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="review-images">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.mVjyO-Njj3fb7OFECgIytwHaFj?w=249&h=187&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" alt="Restaurant Interior 1" class="review-image">
                <img src="https://thearchitectsdiary.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Best-Restaurant-Interior-Design-In-India-3.jpg" alt="Restaurant Interior 2" class="review-image">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/f3/6a/fb/f36afb7c75decde847c8c238aff70e23.jpg" alt="Restaurant Interior 3" class="review-image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="yo"><%- include('partials/footer') %></div>
</body>
</html>
